data.content:

&lt;p&gt;Is it possible to redirect a user to a different page through the use of PHP?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Say the user goes to &lt;code&gt;www.example.com/page.php&lt;/code&gt; and I want to redirect them to &lt;code&gt;www.example.com/index.php&lt;/code&gt;, how would I do so without the use of a meta refresh? Is it possible?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This could even protect my pages from unauthorized users.&lt;/p&gt;
